      "description": "This 2019 Lexus RX 350 is the perfect blend of luxury and reliability, offering a refined driving experience for its next owner. The exterior is finished in a stunning Eminent White Pearl that still holds a deep, glass-like shine; while there are a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with highway driving, the body is straight and free of any significant dents. Inside, the Parchment leather interior has been treated with care\u2014it is smoke-free and the seats remain supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the navigation system, heated seats, and the premium 12-speaker audio system, are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the 3.5L V6 engine runs smoothly and has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule. We have a thick folder of service receipts, including a recent oil change and a fresh brake pad replacement. The tires have plenty of tread remaining, ensuring this vehicle is road-trip ready. It provides a quiet, composed ride that feels as solid as the day it was first driven off the lot.",
